es.usal.bicoverlapper.kernel
Class BiclusterSelection

java.lang.Object
  es.usal.bicoverlapper.kernel.BiclusterSelection

public class BiclusterSelection
extends java.lang.Object

Class with genes and conditions selected, as lists of integers. In case that only a genes are selected. You can choose to leave the condition list empty or to fill it with all the conditions (analogous for conditions)
